_sText:
De_sultan_csgo is a port of the de_sultan map from the Counter-Strike: Global Offensive game.

This map was intensely server tested on a 46 slot server fully loaded with real players for 3 months. 

It has 64 spawn points, two bomb sites, radar overview, loading screen, soundscapes, decent fps, and last but not least it is balanced. 

Enjoy! ps the custom textures may not be used in other maps.
